{"tid":1550190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來彩雲邨唔係淨係得廢老","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:48:58.000Z","uid":258084,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"00e699127621e30ffdb2e8ec25664ee3be898a8b","tid":1550190,"uid":258084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁耐以來都聽唔到有人嗌<br />\n我發夢 今晚特登落樓試一次<br />\n嗌咗一次冇人應 諗住放棄<br />\n點知開始越嚟越多人嗌 有啲人聽到都即刻跑落樓一齊嗌<br />\n最後有兩架狗車過咗嚟 不過冇落車<br />\n嚇到個個都走曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我相信仲會有下次可以再嗌！<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"7a2cf210a603854c3f8d25817c562bb44fd732f8","tid":1550190,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ce6958b3c70577b6af32709f46a2ba369dfe9fb","tid":1550190,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"908 美領見<br />\n幫手推唔該 好撚重要<br />\n文宣嚴重不足！<br />\n[頂置]908必須過百萬，請大家優先開/推908post<br />\n<a href=\"https:/